{"tid":651353,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"有沒「那我懂你意思了」既同好？","createTime":"2018-05-03T04:52:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T18:20:20.000Z","uid":179292,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b8695d01f2c859617f4714f67a6c73c60ac357bd","tid":651353,"uid":179292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-03T04:52:28.000Z","msg":"那我懂你意思了係臺灣獨立搖滾團體，成軍於2007年。<br />\n<br />\n小弟超中意聽佢地，可惜於2016年解散。<br />\n<br />\n唔知呢度有沒同好？<br />\n<br />\nP.s. 「那我懂你意思了」係樂團名，唔係歌名。<br />\n<br />\n沒聽過既埋來介紹返。以下有幾首精選。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://icrvb3jy.xinmedia.com/solomo/article/20632/EC54975C-EFC3-490D-9A96-11395363FED2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ficrvb3jy.xinmedia.com%2Fsolomo%2Farticle%2F20632%2FEC54975C-EFC3-490D-9A96-11395363FED2.jpg&h=cd4f9e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://icrvb3jy.xinmedia.com/solomo/article/61398/D515B66B-48D4-A761-A205-E27560B76B75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ficrvb3jy.xinmedia.com%2Fsolomo%2Farticle%2F61398%2FD515B66B-48D4-A761-A205-E27560B76B75.jpg&h=adad26c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://m13.mask9.com/sites/default/files/styles/l/public/imagepad/20131213/20131213110826-251bc7a71b8aefa96cb787dca11abf3e54889061.55/band-nawodongniyisile-mask9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm13.mask9.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Fl%2Fpublic%2Fimagepad%2F20131213%2F20131213110826-251bc7a71b8aefa96cb787dca11abf3e54889061.55%2Fband-nawodongniyisile-mask9.jpg&h=12004b96&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n那我懂你意思了 - 所以我停下來<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gp6XKEE8B2E&amp;list=PLH68D3zRrrqeCRKJDR6HM5O6tSdcqTcVU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGp6XKEE8B2E%26list%3DPLH68D3zRrrqeCRKJDR6HM5O6tSdcqTcVU&d=hAgi6XNAq8QbtBb1FsP%2BSywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=492a95f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Gp6XKEE8B2E&